{"tid":333404,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人會好驚另一半去一啲自己唔係到嘅活動？","createTime":"2017-07-23T18:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T04:10:24.000Z","uid":55122,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1451cb6f6bb63e136d82fb8890de1eefdf6ab9","tid":333404,"uid":55122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:48:34.000Z","msg":"例如 唱K 去一大班佢嘅fd嘅聚會之類<br />\n唔好講單獨 一大班有男有女都已經內心唔知點解會有啲抵觸 唔知點解硬係覺得好唔安樂<br />\n但內心又好肯定唔會發生啲乜 帽啊 比人摸水啊 呢啲  <br />\n一方面會覺得如果表現到好限制佢 自己就覺得好似唔係咁好 佢亦到好唔鍾意比人限 覺得自己正常社交 我都覺得都係 但一方面就會覺得有啲抵觸 不安 唔舒服<br />\n搞到好辛苦 好似人格分裂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW 全同性就無問題<br />\n1999 唔知大家明唔明 想聽下大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c99f2408c1e6e2e3006eb1d193b189948ac4b1","tid":333404,"uid":55122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T19:23:31.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bfa8d65fa9068a4e70532f2812be7614afb79c","tid":333404,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T19:38:59.000Z","msg":"點都有些少<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e458201b4f294280d855eaa9c2d21e16451c298d","tid":333404,"uid":55122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T19:53:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點都有些少<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 其實我都係好愛佢太緊張佢先會咁<br />\n我反而覺得大方無乜野 佢個心只會 哦~比我去 而唔會諗我係會有啲唔舒服 呷醋 但我最後都比妳去係有幾掙扎 <br />\n同佢講呢啲問題 唔比佢去 就屌9我 唔比佢正常社交 限制佢乜乜乜 又嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320561dd865b152748ebe1d4b38af88f8b701898","tid":333404,"uid":128060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T19:57:47.000Z","msg":"都係一個信字<br />\n同埋係你嘅就係你<br />\n唔係你嘅都無辦法<br />\n搵返個有安全感㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89725c3dd04c2cfb143fad7d4a6809f3105adaf3","tid":333404,"uid":55122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T20:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係一個信字<br />\n同埋係你嘅就係你<br />\n唔係你嘅都無辦法<br />\n搵返個有安全感㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁諗係好事 但背叛果一刻嘅感覺我不敢想像<br />\nBTW一段感情入面總有一個愛得比對方更多<br />\n而往往果個都係傷得最深跌得最痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effde6975fed6a61921c56b2ed91f64c63b862f1","tid":333404,"uid":61900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1458c5c0e7a8035b6f40aabc5ea2864c5e95fe4b","tid":333404,"uid":61900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5e314d15efb95b36fab4a313748cafd456314e","tid":333404,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:10:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}